SEctiOn 4 - prArtthanA, kShamA prArtthanA 
1. sUryaM sundaralOkanAthamamRutaM vEdAntasAraM Sivam | 
j~jAnaM brahmamayaM surESamamalaM lOkaikacittaM svayam | 
indrAdityanarAdhipaM suraguruM trailOkyacUDAmaNim | 
viShNu brahmaSiva svarUpahRudayaM vandE sadA BAskaram || 

2. BAnO BAskara mArttANDa caNDaraSmE divAkara | 
AyurArOgyamaiSvaryaM SriyaM putrAMSca dEhi mE || 

3. dhRuta padmadvayaM BAnuM tEjOmaNDala maddhyagam | 
sar^vAdhivyAdhi SamanaM CAyASliShTatanuM BajE || 

4. sauryamaNDala maddhyasthaM sAMbaM saMsAraBEShajam | 
nIlagrIvaM virUpAkShaM namAmi Sivamavyayam || 

5. namO dharmavidhAnAya namastE kRutasAkShiNE | 
namaH pratyakSha dEvAya BAskarAya namO namaH || 

6. anyathA SaraNaM nAsti tvamEva SaraNaM mama | 
tasmAt kAruNyaBAvEna rakSha rakSha divAkara || 

7. Adityasya namaskArAn yE kur^vanti dinE dinE | 
janmAntara sahasrEShu dAridraM nOpajAyatE || 

8. yadakShara padaBraShTaM mAtrAhInaM tu yad BavEt | 
tath sar^vaM kShamyatAM dEva divAkara namO&stu tE || 

9. visarga bindu mAtrANi padapAdAkSharANi ca | 
nyUnAni cAtiriktAni kShamasva ca divAkara || 

